{"tid":2118912,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[放榜又要回帶] 「想升grade」唔係Retake的理由，「可以升grade」才是Retake的理由","createTime":"2020-07-21T20:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T23:35:37.000Z","uid":10298,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"650a4464bb2ac2ac5813680db8d88a164cc0c245","tid":2118912,"uid":10298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T20:29:24.000Z","msg":"「想升grade」唔係Retake的理由，「可以升grade」才是Retake的理由。By Outlier <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/outlierseconomics/index/dse/retake_upgrade\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Foutlierseconomics%2Findex%2Fdse%2Fretake_upgrade&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rjwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=b19b2c2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/outlierseconomics/index/dse/retake_upgrade</a><br />\n<br />\n希望有心Retake嘅同學仔睇咗佢先<br />\n我由第一屆開始考 經歷過兩次Retake<br />\n到依家過咗八年 都係覺得呢篇文最寫實<br />\n亦係最能夠描述我曾經失敗過嘅嗰種原因同心態<br />\n<br />\n基本上所謂Retake Tritake 副學位 <br />\n到最後入U我都經歷過<br />\n如果有同學仔真係想要個有經驗嘅建議<br />\n可以留個言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外推到Outlier入嚟<br />\n再次多謝你2013年寫咗呢篇文"},{"pid":"0ed65d088f8477728a2548a337ade7a70afae0f9","tid":2118912,"uid":220677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T20:37:53.000Z","msg":"Retake Tritake之後幾多分"},{"pid":"fcacfc0d654e9fc721f8af452a34e8af957b9b8d","tid":2118912,"uid":10298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ed65d088f8477728a2548a337ade7a70afae0f9","tid":2118912,"uid":220677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T20:37:53.000Z","msg":"Retake Tritake之後幾多分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T20:42:56.000Z","msg":"第一次16&gt;17<br />\n第二次17&gt;24<br />\nBest 5"},{"pid":"126bd33651872db3debbb21390cb7fb762b93885","tid":2118912,"uid":10298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T20:52:31.000Z","msg":"苦口婆心都要講句<br />\n唔好見連登好似好多retake升幾分<br />\n就覺得唔難做到<br />\n呢個係倖存者偏差<br />\n做到嘅人自己會出post話你知 <br />\n自然睇落成功例子唔少<br />\n<br />\n但係數據唔會呃人<br />\n即使撇除一班真係唔讀書嘅retaker之後<br />\n成功機會都係好細<br />\n<br />\nRetake係講求 勤力 資質 前學校背景 朋友學習氛圍 對自己能力嘅判斷 自律性 規劃 好多好多<br />\n喺做呢個決定之前真係好好諗清楚先<br />\n因為你揀咗自修 你係用咗一年時間去投資<br />\n同你去讀asso hd係絕對唔一樣"},{"pid":"5be6cd7abe24199b751026cc5dc907a5874d1895","tid":2118912,"uid":3852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T22:45:31.000Z","msg":"完全冇諗過retake<br />\n讀Asso升返三大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f207f90a18d2be280cc47a4fd8ceb6b214cc44","tid":2118912,"uid":10298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T23:21:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a2aa92a0c0aaf8c6c0f2ac8387eda28e79f99fd","tid":2118912,"uid":10298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T23:21:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b20edabe85ea4594cf47cd47a54a50e3fe5d356","tid":2118912,"uid":178660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T23:35:37.000Z","msg":"push"}]}